<P>
   Here are the stories New York Times editors are planning for
Monday, Nov. 16, Page 1. The N.Y. Times News Service Night
Supervisor is Tim Hilchey; phone: (888) 346-9867; e-mail:
hilchey(at)nytimes.com.
