honored significantly.''
</P>
<P>
   ``I don't know whether in the back of their minds is the idea
that, God forbid, anything happens to them he would take over the
moral education of the child.''
</P>
<P>
   &UR; WHOLE PERSONALS GIFT CATALOG &LR;
