   __ Our mistake thinking the new Bruins basketball press guide
was going to be more than Steve Lavin's family album. . .
</P>
<P>
   __ Riddle me this, Bratman: Why, if UCLA already plays all its
home games at the Rose Bowl, does it make it such a big deal about
trying to get to the Rose Bowl every season? . .
</P>
