   __ CSUN's biggest hoopfest in years _ Tuesday's public offering
at the University of Tennessee _ will be heard on zero local radio
stations. . .
</P>
<P>
   __ RIP, Ralphie Valladares. . .
</P>
<P>
   __ Today's trivia question: Oksana Baiul, who finally turns
drinking age (21) today, was born in what Ukraine city?. . .
</P>
<P>
   __ Trivia answer: If you said Dnepropetrovsk, bless yourself,
and you're correct. And try saying that after a few Vodka and
tonics. . .
</P>
<P>
   __ An ESPN Chilton Sports Poll in October asked more than 1,000
sports fans if they were interested in sports more or less compared
to this time last year. ``Same'' (43.5 percent) won out over
``more'' (35 percent), and of those who said ``less'' (22 percent),
almost a third said it was because they had no time and were too
busy rather than they were turned off by salaries or league
lockouts/strikes.
</P>
